DESCRIPTION: This PHP snippet shows how to send an email campaign right away by configuring Brevo client authentication and calling the sendEmailCampaignNow method. It needs the Brevo PHP SDK, GuzzleHttp, and a valid campaign ID. On execution, the method sends the campaign; errors are captured and output via exception handling.
